<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />These are things that we have heard and learned,</para>

<para style="q1">things that our ancestors have told us.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />We will not keep them from their descendants.</para>

<para style="q1">We will tell the next generation about the praiseworthy deeds of Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">his strength, and the wonders that he has done.</para>
